description:
Understanding what the Bible says about baptism is vital to our salvation. However, many sincere Christians are confused on this critical topic. This thrilling, full-production video will reveal 10 essential facts about baptism!

Many are desiring to give their lives fully to Jesus, but wonder if baptism essential to salvation. What does baptism symbolize? What is the true Biblical method of baptism? What must be done along WITH baptism? Does baptism involve joining a church? What does the Bible say about re-baptism? Let’s go right to the Bible to learn these 10 facts about baptism!
